      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Knights of Golarion travel far and wide combating evil, but in ambiguous situations, they need to be certain that the foes they smite truly deserve it. You gain the ability to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.universal-creature-rules.Item.hcyevxAeVNkcrWSE]{detect alignment} twice per day as per the universal creature rule as a move action. Targets can attempt a @Check[type:will]{Will saving throw} (DC = 10 + your level + your key ability modifier)[[10 + @details.level.value + @data.attributes.keyability]] to negate this effect.</p>"
